data.description: Come see this stunning 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home in Snellville. On the main level, you will find gorgeous LVP flooring with an open floor plan that makes this home great for entertaining family and friends. The family room with fireplace leads right into the formal dining room. The updated kitchen features stainless steel appliances, an island with breakfast bar, and a pantry. The spacious primary bedroom includes bay windows, a walk-in closet, dual vanities, and a jetted soaking tub. Upstairs, you will also find 3 secondary bedrooms, another full bathroom, and a convenient upstairs laundry room. Relax and enjoy your morning coffee or evening beverage from the sun room at the back of the house. Fenced backyard is perfect for kids or pets. Ask how you can receive up to $1500 credit by using one of our preferred lenders. Exclusions may apply.
